    "title": "Why is Quick-Commerce gaining rapid success in India?",
    "tag": "DevOps",
    "cover": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*ly2ZO2X1eX0KXzDUyKax5g.png",
    "readTime": "3 min read",
    "content": "<p id=\"0a4f\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph adj adk xv adl b adm adn ado adp adq adr ads adt adu adv adw adx ady adz aea aeb aec aed aee aef aeg or cj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 2.14em; margin-bottom: -0.46em; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-family: source-serif-pro, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Let me start from the beginning. When I read in the news like –</p><p id=\"fa7e\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph adj adk xv adl b adm adn ado adp adq adr ads adt adu adv adw adx ady adz aea aeb aec aed aee aef aeg or cj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 2.14em; margin-bottom: -0.46em; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-family: source-serif-pro, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">· Blinkit Leads the Quick Commerce Race with 40% Market Share and 122% Year-over-Year Growth</p><p id=\"d3ae\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph adj adk xv adl b adm adn ado adp adq adr ads adt adu adv adw adx ady adz aea aeb aec aed aee aef aeg or cj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 2.14em; margin-bottom: -0.46em; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-family: source-serif-pro, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">· Zepto’s Meteoric Rise: From 15% to 30% Market Share in Just Two Years</p><p id=\"f955\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph adj adk xv adl b adm adn ado adp adq adr ads adt adu adv adw adx ady adz aea aeb aec aed aee aef aeg or cj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 2.14em; margin-bottom: -0.46em; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-family: source-serif-pro, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">· Quick commerce market grew by over 280% in just two years (FY 2021–22 to FY 2023–24)</p><p id=\"bf5d\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph adj adk xv adl b adm adn ado adp adq adr ads adt adu adv adw adx ady adz aea aeb aec aed aee aef aeg or cj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 2.14em; margin-bottom: -0.46em; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-family: source-serif-pro, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">I was shocked by reading that Zomato — a startup valued at more than 10 billion USD, acquired BlinkIt — A q-commerce startup, and now its valuation is more than that of its parent company, Zomato. The fact that Giant E-commerce like Amazon and Flipkart grew nearly 10x from $3.9 billion in 2009 to $38 billion in 2017, while Q-commerce expanded 6.7x from $500 million in FY2021–22 to $3.34 billion in FY2023–24, showcasing its rapid growth trajectory.</p><p id=\"6f1d\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph adj adk xv adl b adm adn ado adp adq adr ads adt adu adv adw adx ady adz aea aeb aec aed aee aef aeg or cj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 2.14em; margin-bottom: -0.46em; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-family: source-serif-pro, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Let’s first understand this.</p><h2 id=\"ad75\" class=\"aeh aei xv am aej pz aek qa qh qi ael qj qq qr aem qs qz ra aen rb ri rj aeo rk rr aep cj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.95em; margin-bottom: -0.28em; font-family: sohne, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); line-height: 30px; letter-spacing: -0.016em; font-size: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">What is Quick Commerce?</h2><p id=\"fb3f\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph adj adk xv adl b adm aeq ado adp adq aer ads adt adu aes adw adx ady aet aea aeb aec aeu aee aef aeg or cj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0.94em; margin-bottom: -0.46em; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-family: source-serif-pro, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Q-commerce, or quick commerce, is the next step in the evolution of e-commerce. Unlike traditional online shopping, where delivery times can range from a few hours to days, Q-commerce focuses on delivering products in extremely short time frames — usually within 10 to 30 minutes.</p><p id=\"ec22\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph adj adk xv adl b adm adn ado adp adq adr ads adt adu adv adw adx ady adz aea aeb aec aed aee aef aeg or cj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 2.14em; margin-bottom: -0.46em; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-family: source-serif-pro, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"adl hi\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">So, what events paved the way for the rise of Q-commerce startups?</span></p><p id=\"6204\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph adj adk xv adl b adm adn ado adp adq adr ads adt adu adv adw adx ady adz aea aeb aec aed aee aef aeg or cj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 2.14em; margin-bottom: -0.46em; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-family: source-serif-pro, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Back in the days when Amazon and Flipkart were dominating the e-commerce market. After COVID-19, during the pandemic, the Indian government strictly quarantined everyone by not letting anyone out in public. Everything was close, so people started spending time online, from social meetings, work, and education to shopping. People’s interest in buying over e-commerce increased immensely, heavily impacting local store owners. In a country like India, these local stores were their source of income, affecting millions of people.</p><figure class=\"aew aex aey aez afa add acv acw paragraph-image\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 56px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; font-size: medium; clear: both; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div class=\"acv acw aev\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; max-width: 640px;\"><picture style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><source srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*TKuTSwBFr5codVlDzHc_6w.jpeg 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*TKuTSwBFr5codVlDzHc_6w.jpeg 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*TKuTSwBFr5codVlDzHc_6w.jpeg 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*TKuTSwBFr5codVlDzHc_6w.jpeg 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*TKuTSwBFr5codVlDzHc_6w.jpeg 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*TKuTSwBFr5codVlDzHc_6w.jpeg 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1280/format:webp/1*TKuTSwBFr5codVlDzHc_6w.jpeg 1280w\" sizes=\"(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 640px\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><source data-testid=\"og\" srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*TKuTSwBFr5codVlDzHc_6w.jpeg 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*TKuTSwBFr5codVlDzHc_6w.jpeg 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*TKuTSwBFr5codVlDzHc_6w.jpeg 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*TKuTSwBFr5codVlDzHc_6w.jpeg 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*TKuTSwBFr5codVlDzHc_6w.jpeg 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*TKuTSwBFr5codVlDzHc_6w.jpeg 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1280/1*TKuTSwBFr5codVlDzHc_6w.jpeg 1280w\" sizes=\"(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 640px\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"f acg adi c\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" loading=\"lazy\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:960/1*TKuTSwBFr5codVlDzHc_6w.jpeg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: middle; width: 640px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"></picture></div></figure><p id=\"e89e\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph adj adk xv adl b adm adn ado adp adq adr ads adt adu adv adw adx ady adz aea aeb aec aed aee aef aeg or cj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 2.14em; margin-bottom: -0.46em; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-family: source-serif-pro, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Millions of shop owners across several Indian cities participated in protests against these e-commerce giants. Protesters used slogans like “Walmart Go Back” and called Jeff Bezos an “economic terrorist.” They demanded that the government block deals like Walmart’s acquisition of Flipkart. The government also backed these local store owners by starting “Vocal for Local” initiatives. These protests and government statements raised concerns about the potential impact of foreign direct investment in India’s retail sector.</p><figure class=\"aew aex aey aez afa add acv acw paragraph-image\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 56px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; font-size: medium; clear: both; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"ade adf bl adg f adh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; width: 680px; position: relative; cursor: zoom-in; z-index: auto; transition: transform 300ms cubic-bezier(0.2, 0, 0.2, 1);\"><span class=\"bm bn bo u bp bq br bs bt speechify-ignore\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: -1px; position: absolute; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden; clip: rect(0px, 0px, 0px, 0px); text-wrap-mode: nowrap; border-width: 0px;\">Press enter or click to view image in full size</span><div class=\"acv acw afb\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; max-width: 800px;\"><picture style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><source srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*HPTv_tLfrZKZzoj1leEZJw.jpeg 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*HPTv_tLfrZKZzoj1leEZJw.jpeg 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*HPTv_tLfrZKZzoj1leEZJw.jpeg 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*HPTv_tLfrZKZzoj1leEZJw.jpeg 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*HPTv_tLfrZKZzoj1leEZJw.jpeg 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*HPTv_tLfrZKZzoj1leEZJw.jpeg 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/1*HPTv_tLfrZKZzoj1leEZJw.jpeg 1400w\" sizes=\"(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" type=\"image/webp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><source data-testid=\"og\" srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*HPTv_tLfrZKZzoj1leEZJw.jpeg 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*HPTv_tLfrZKZzoj1leEZJw.jpeg 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*HPTv_tLfrZKZzoj1leEZJw.jpeg 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*HPTv_tLfrZKZzoj1leEZJw.jpeg 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*HPTv_tLfrZKZzoj1leEZJw.jpeg 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*HPTv_tLfrZKZzoj1leEZJw.jpeg 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*HPTv_tLfrZKZzoj1leEZJw.jpeg 1400w\" sizes=\"(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"f acg adi c\" width=\"700\" height=\"396\" loading=\"lazy\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1050/1*HPTv_tLfrZKZzoj1leEZJw.jpeg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: middle; width: 680px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"></picture></div></div></figure><p id=\"a082\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph adj adk xv adl b adm adn ado adp adq adr ads adt adu adv adw adx ady adz aea aeb aec aed aee aef aeg or cj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 2.14em; margin-bottom: -0.46em; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-family: source-serif-pro, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">While these multi-billion-dollar companies were struggling to find a solution to these problems, the founders of Zepto and Blinkit understood the issues and came up with an out-of-the-box idea of quick commerce to solve them.</p><div class=\"nt g\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 24px; font-size: medium; display: flex; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div class=\"q\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><a class=\"bc ak be cp bg an bh u ao ap aq ar as at au g\" rel=\"noopener follow\" href=\"https://medium.com/download-app?source=promotion_paragraph---post_body_banner_surround_blocks--be53a453c878---------------------------------------\" data-discover=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; display: flex; fill: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; cursor: pointer; font-size: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; border: inherit;\"><picture style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(max-width: 551.98px)\" srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/da:true/resize:fit:0/c712ccda454f1457503a26381419ec4fcad2dacc1bba1be13158975b5a6d3ab9\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(min-width: 552px) and (max-width: 727.98px)\" srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/da:true/resize:fit:0/c712ccda454f1457503a26381419ec4fcad2dacc1bba1be13158975b5a6d3ab9\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(min-width: 728px) and (max-width: 903.98px)\" srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/da:true/resize:fit:0/58dbc9043bb7d1ca1cc3a9bda27b9b94f96c34a37d6e1cb5b47ba882e5cde883\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(min-width: 904px) and (max-width: 1079.98px)\" srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/da:true/resize:fit:0/58dbc9043bb7d1ca1cc3a9bda27b9b94f96c34a37d6e1cb5b47ba882e5cde883\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><source media=\"(min-width: 1080px)\" srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/da:true/resize:fit:0/58dbc9043bb7d1ca1cc3a9bda27b9b94f96c34a37d6e1cb5b47ba882e5cde883\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><img alt=\"Download the Medium app\" class=\"f\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: middle; width: 680px;\"></picture></a></div></div><p id=\"4933\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph adj adk xv adl b adm ado adp adq ads adt adu adw adx ady aea aeb aec aee aef nt aeg or cj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: -0.46em; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-family: source-serif-pro, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">So, let’s go through the problem Q-commerce is solving,</p><p id=\"c0f8\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph adj adk xv adl b adm adn ado adp adq adr ads adt adu adv adw adx ady adz aea aeb aec aed aee aef aeg or cj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 2.14em; margin-bottom: -0.46em; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-family: source-serif-pro, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The Q-commerce business model relies on partnering with local stores, turning them into micro-fulfillment centers to enable seemingly impossible 10-minute delivery times. This approach helped address the challenges faced by local store owners. By giving them an online presence and good business to sell their products.</p><p id=\"50f6\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph adj adk xv adl b adm adn ado adp adq adr ads adt adu adv adw adx ady adz aea aeb aec aed aee aef aeg or cj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 2.14em; margin-bottom: -0.46em; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-family: source-serif-pro, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In this fast-paced world, people are becoming impatient to order anything online. And this is also useful when you are too busy to go shopping. In particular, people are more inclined toward shopping online than conventional shopping.</p><p id=\"8002\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph adj adk xv adl b adm adn ado adp adq adr ads adt adu adv adw adx ady adz aea aeb aec aed aee aef aeg or cj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 2.14em; margin-bottom: -0.46em; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-family: source-serif-pro, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">This solution creates a win-win scenario for both customers and local business owners.</p><p id=\"4ff2\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph adj adk xv adl b adm adn ado adp adq adr ads adt adu adv adw adx ady adz aea aeb aec aed aee aef aeg or cj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 2.14em; margin-bottom: -0.46em; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-family: source-serif-pro, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">For more, Let’s ask one more question:</p><p id=\"f176\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph adj adk xv adl b adm adn ado adp adq adr ads adt adu adv adw adx ady adz aea aeb aec aed aee aef aeg or cj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 2.14em; margin-bottom: -0.46em; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-family: source-serif-pro, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">How are they delivering anything in 10 minutes? This is impossible. You can not provide anything at that time when you are living in a very population-dense urban area in India. I was like, How are they making this possible?</p><p id=\"276a\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph adj adk xv adl b adm adn ado adp adq adr ads adt adu adv adw adx ady adz aea aeb aec aed aee aef aeg or cj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 2.14em; margin-bottom: -0.46em; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-family: source-serif-pro, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">This is made possible by:</p><p id=\"f981\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph adj adk xv adl b adm adn ado adp adq adr ads adt adu adv adw adx ady adz aea aeb aec aed aee aef aeg or cj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 2.14em; margin-bottom: -0.46em; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-family: source-serif-pro, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1.&nbsp;<span class=\"adl hi\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">Small Fulfillment Centers:</span>&nbsp;Located close to customers, these hubs store a limited variety of high-demand items like groceries, snacks, and household essentials.</p><p id=\"dc8a\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph adj adk xv adl b adm adn ado adp adq adr ads adt adu adv adw adx ady adz aea aeb aec aed aee aef aeg or cj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 2.14em; margin-bottom: -0.46em; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-family: source-serif-pro, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2.&nbsp;<span class=\"adl hi\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">Last-Mile Delivery Networks:</span>&nbsp;A fleet of delivery agents or autonomous vehicles ensures fast, efficient delivery.</p><p id=\"d642\" class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph adj adk xv adl b adm adn ado adp adq adr ads adt adu adv adw adx ady adz aea aeb aec aed aee aef aeg or cj\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 2.14em; margin-bottom: -0.46em; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-family: source-serif-pro, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3.&nbsp;<span class=\"adl hi\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">Advanced Technology:</span>&nbsp;AI and predictive analytics help companies anticipate customer needs, optimize inventory, and streamline delivery routes.</p>",
